<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><b>Due to data protection, I am not able to confirm any details about another customer</b>. <br><br>However, I can confirm that <b>vouchers for a successful referral will be sent 28 days after your friends policy start date</b>.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">You may be able to get more detailed information by speaking directly to your friend.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">If you have any further questions, please do not hesitate to get in touch.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">T: 01242 808 740</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>